yard	linear	3 ft
yd	alias	yard

hand	linear	4 in
fathom	linear	2 yard
chain	linear	11 fathom
furlong	linear	10 chain
mile	linear	8 furlong
mi	alias	mile
league	linear	3 mile

# area
acre	linear	chain furlong

# volume
